Traveling all over the world.

00:25:08.020 --> 00:25:13.531
He's now in-- Just did a report yesterday
on the Foxconn workers for Apple and all the

00:25:13.531 --> 00:25:14.531
issues.

00:25:14.531 --> 00:25:15.531
He's traveling all over.

